short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Save more on all Online shopping stores over and above all discounts and coupons. Get Upto 10% Cashback on your all online purchases

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Shopibin Cashback allows you to save upto 10% for your online purchases in form of Cashback from almost all online stores. Just press Ctrl+M while you are on store website and the extension will open and reload the page again. It's Done.
Extension will also remind you to press Ctrl+M when you are visiting any online store and is smart enough to remember it's own position so that it doesn't ruin your shopping experience.
You will get cashback for your purchase in Shopibin Account. Visit Shopibin Site to redeem your cashback earned. 
Refer your friends to Shopibin and earn more.
